## Data Cleaning & Preparation
python
Copy code
# Convert date column
sales_df['Sale_Date'] = pd.to_datetime(sales_df['Sale_Date'])

# Extract date components
sales_df['Year'] = sales_df['Sale_Date'].dt.year
sales_df['Month'] = sales_df['Sale_Date'].dt.month

# Clean text columns
customers_df['Customer_Name'] = customers_df['Customer_Name'].str.title()
customers_df['City'] = customers_df['City'].str.title()
## Merge Sales & Customer Data (Mandatory Requirement)
python
Copy code
merged_df = pd.merge(
    sales_df,
    customers_df,
    on="Customer_ID",
    how="inner"
)

merged_df.head()
