## Customer Retention Rate (Advanced Analysis)
python
Copy code
customer_purchase_count = merged_df['Customer_ID'].value_counts()

retention_rate = (
    customer_purchase_count[customer_purchase_count > 1].count()
    / customer_purchase_count.count()
) * 100

retention_rate
